author: Jesse J. Holland, Associated Press
title: Black men gathering for Million Man March 20th anniversary
text: Photo: Doug Mills, AP FILE - In this Monday, Oct. 16, 1995 file photo, Nation of Islam leader Louis Farrakhan addresses the Million Man March from Capitol Hill in Washington. FILE - In this Monday, Oct. 16, 1995 file photo, Nation of Islam... WASHINGTON (AP) — Black men from around the nation are gathering on the National Mall to celebrate the 20th anniversary of the Million Man March and call for policing reforms and changes in black communities.
